summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Thirty-third Avenue form the north margin of East Pike Street to the north margin of East Pike Street et al in the City of Seattle, by paving with asphalt under Ordinance No. 20376, creating Local Improvement District No. 1971 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
